How to use:

```
const { Tailwind } = VM.require("klngrs.near/widget/Tailwind") || {
  TailwindWrapper: () => <></>,
};

return (
<Tailwind>
    <button className="px-7 py-4 text-white duration-150 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-500 active:bg-indigo-700">Button</button>
</Tailwind>
)
```

(See https://near.org/klngrs.near/widget/FloatUiWidget)
